Invocation Name: fang stocks
des:
Do you want to know how your FANG stocks are doing today? Just say “Alexa, Fang Stocks” and you will get a a market update on all of the FANG stocks plus Tesla.

**Disclaimer: The information provided by FANG Stocks is for general purposes only and should not be relied on for trading purposes.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
